auma, Musculoskeletal Problems,      Carpal Tunnel Syndrome,&nbsp; etc.</p>    <p>Read for example this Wikipedia article: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer-induced_medical_problems">Computer-induced
        medical problems</a></p>    <br>  </body></html>